title: BONUS EPISODE: Taylor Bennett Talks Black Music History + New Project "Coming of Age."
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Taylor Bennett stopped by Ebro in the Morning to have a very good discussion on the influence of Black music in its history, being independent, his thoughts of rap music today, how to better express himself in the music and projecting positivity, his brother Chance the Rapper and much more. His project 'Coming of Age ' is available now! 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
